# Responses to a major suit opening

# C = ♣
# D = ♦
# H = ♥
# S = ♠

2♣ NJx => 5+ x, 2 of top 3 in x;
    test AQxxx xxx xxx xx:
        2♣ 2S;

2♣ 2N => 8+ tpts, partial_stoppers unbid;
    test Qx Kxxx Kxxx Jxx:
        2♣ 2N;
  
2♣ 2D => always;
    test xx Kxxx xxxx xxx:
        2♣ 2D;
        